:::'''Robin:''' Don't be. The manager doesn't have to be on stage. They just need to ensure the band's performance goes without a hitch.
:::{{tx}}
::;(Return to previous option selection)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why me?
:::'''Robin:''' We've known each other a long time. Of course I'm going to trust in your conduct and capability.
:::{{tx}}
